Dwarf workers can be upgraded by spending iron.
The Dvala can use diamonds to scry for new mines or create Rune Smiths.
Rune Smiths can use gems to create elite guards and warriors.
The Councilor can call forth a new Dvala by spending a heap of gold.
Human mercenaries often offer their services, but at high prices.
Humans recruited at special locations cost twice the gold.
Minus 1 gold/iron/gem income from non mines."
